defaultPaul defaultSmeedefault: The evidence so far is that first-time buyers are those who have been expressing interest in these warehouse loans. If you look traditionally, historically, those who have been drawn to the 95% LTV band have been the first-time buyer. I would be surprised if, when the scheme is fully up and running next year, we did not see most of the loans going towards the first-time buyer end.
